हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Toxic Rich Baby follows Ojal Mehra, a woman betrayed by her husband Arnav, mocked by his brother Rutvik, and humiliated by the powerful Ranjit and cunning Avani. But beneath her scars lies the secret identity of Lady Nova Vale a fearless warrior with power, dignity, and unbreakable spirit. With the loyal Jai by her side and the mysterious Vikram reentering her life, Ojal rises from heartbreak to reclaim her inheritance, her honor, and her destiny.
